text: Bikramjit Debnath (born 26 December 1998) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Tripura in the 2018–19 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 19 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Tripura cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
